caption: Food is delicious. Can't go wrong with anything you order. Only problem is that chef doesn't always wear mask while cooking and in these times it is imperative.  Also the cashier grabbed fries with her hand while packing up an order and utensils should be used.
Best chickeng wings ever, I get them every weekend and they're always on point, costumer service is the best, Definitely recommended 👌

Best wings in queens. Takes me 50min to get here from home but I will come back when I can. Garlic pepper is awesome lemon pepper is quite nice too. I think I'll try the honey garlic pepper next time.

I've been here 4 times, each time for pickup I've had a variety of flavors and never been let down. My fav is always the classic Buffalo spicy,  tastes amazing and always made fresh. Great food l, Great customer service. I'd def recommend. Shrimp fried rice is also legit.

Best wing spot I've been to. Buffalo wings are on point, so are the lemon pepper wings. This place puts wingstop to shame. When you call for pickup, if you  tell them how far away you are, they will make the food to be fresh for your arrival. Customer service is excellent as well
I went to try their wings, but got really impressed with their fried rice. The wings combo with fried rice is a 1-2 punch. Highly recommended!!
